metadata.description:
That might be enough to go to North Carolina, Duke, but UCLA, Kentucky, Kansas, Connecticut, don't they?



At the very least, Illinois State and even the University of Washington are better than Marquette.



When he arrived at Marquette, he didn't know what to say when he got the news.



So, is Deena a retard, too?
